<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, width=device-width">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style/navigation.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style/auth.css">
    <title>WE Calendar</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="nav">
        <div class="nav-title">
            WE Calendar
        </div>
        <div class="nav-menu">
            <button type="button" class="menu-button" onclick="location.href='/'">Home</button>
            <button type="button" class="menu-button" onclick="location.href='/create'">Create</button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section class="main">
        <h1 id="authTitle">안녕하세요! 티켓 검사 있겠습니다.</h1>
        <h2 id="authSubTitle">아래에 보안코드를 입력해주세요.</h2>
        <form id="authForm" method="POST" action='/schedule/'>
            <input type="text" id="authCode" name="authCode" value="<%=authCode%>" hidden>
            <input type="text" id="scheduleId" name="scheduleId" value="<%=scheduleId%>" hidden>
            <input type="text" id="inputCode" name="inputCode" autocomplete="off">
            
            <button id="authSubmit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </section>
</body>
<script>
    if(<%=isFail%> == true) {
        alert('보안코드가 틀렸습니다. 다시 입력해주세요.');
    }
    document.getElementById('authCode').value = '<%=authCode%>';
</script>
</html>